static/js/scripts.js
- Contains JavaScript code for client-side interactivity, such as button actions and form validations.

data/
- Stores all application data in text files as specified.
- Each file corresponds to a data category (users, courses, enrollments, assignments, submissions, certificates).
- The backend reads from and writes to these files to persist application state.
